summary:
A professional with 10+ experience in Process Improvements, Business Analysis, Agile Development & Digital Transformation. 

Sietse is team player with strong communicative skills. Passionate about improving, designing and building digital client experiences. 

Working as a Business Consultant within the Financial Services sector has allowed him to gain experience at a number of financial institutions, working in various departments and different topics. Working in Amsterdam, London and Singapore gave the opportunity to work with different team sizes and cultures. 

Roles typically involved being the bridge between business and IT, driving strategic initiatives from ideation to Agile implementation and Go-Live.  

Experience in:

* Process Improvements (by applying lean management principles)
* Agile Development (acted as Business Analyst and Product Owner)
* Proces Digitization & Creating of innovative POC's with AI/Machine learning)
* Change Management
* Business Strategy and Analysis (e.g. creating solution option/benchmarking papers for management)
